meanings.definition: A person who specializes in aquatint printing.
meanings.sent1: The talented aquatinters at the studio create beautiful prints.
meanings.sent2: The aquatinters showcased their latest works at the art exhibition.
meanings.sent3: The aquatinters had a friendly competition to see who could make the most unique print.
meanings.sent4: Her mind was an aquatinters' workshop, full of creativity and precision.
meanings.sent5: The aquatinters' hands moved swiftly, turning blank paper into works of art.
